{"tid":1690140,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"馬逢國被防暴警察截查","createTime":"2019-11-03T07:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T09:56:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":150,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"30a3ca91fb954ed5d29304be3e28ec7b4268a1bb","tid":1690140,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191103/s00001/e012841a0bcb456f8124d17d852cdc04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191103%2Fs00001%2Fe012841a0bcb456f8124d17d852cdc04.jpg&h=2338cd4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網民發起今午（3日）「反警暴七區行街」行動。<br />\n<br />\n【14:27】屯門政府合署附近一度有約30名示威者聚集，防暴警察到場後示威者四散。有年輕男子被防暴警察截查，街坊隨即指罵警察。防暴警察逗留約6分鐘後收隊。<br />\n<br />\n【14:21】立法會體育、演藝、文化及出版界議員馬逢國行經金鐘海富天橋時，被防暴警察截停及問他前往何處，另一名防暴警察認出他後放行。<br />\n<br />\n【14:17】市民方先生表示，今日到金鐘添馬公園本想看海，卻遭警方驅趕，又問「佢哋（警察）張身分證值錢過我張身分證？」中區警區總督察陳淑萍說，因可能有公眾活動，封閉範圍包括海富天橋，稱市民可到其他公園活動。<br />\n<br />\n【14:05】防暴警察推進至金鐘海富天橋後一度停下，數名長者繼續指罵警員，警方續推進，表示在海富天橋的人也要離開。<br />\n<br />\n【13:58】防暴警察從金鐘添馬公園海濱開始推進，要求市民立即離開，引起市民不滿，有市民表示「皇軍都唔會咁」。<br />\n<br />\n【13:52】現場廣播稱由於有公眾活動，金鐘添馬公園將會關閉，大批防暴警察要求在場者離開。<br />\n<br />\n【13:20】下午1時，旺角麥花臣遊樂場外有至少20名防暴警察及便衣警員駐守，球場內暫時所見只有外傭聚集。<br />\n<br />\n1時15分左右，金鐘添馬公園約10多名防暴警察巡查，向在場外傭稱添馬公園稍後或有集會，促外傭下午3時前離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191103/s00001/1572758184297/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E3%80%8C%E8%A1%8C%E8%A1%97%E3%80%8D-%E6%B7%BB%E9%A6%AC%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89-%E9%BA%A5%E8%8A%B1%E8%87%A3%E9%81%8A%E6%A8%82%E5%A0%B4%E6%9C%89%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E9%A7%90%E5%AE%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191103%2Fs00001%2F1572758184297%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25A1%2597%25E3%2580%258D-%25E6%25B7%25BB%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%2596%2589-%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E8%258A%25B1%25E8%2587%25A3%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%25A7%2590%25E5%25AE%2588&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=8b092253\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191103%2Fs00001%2F1572758184297%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25A1%2597%25E3%2580%258D-%25E6%25B7%25BB%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%2596%2589-%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E8%258A%25B1%25E8%2587%25A3%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%25A7%2590%25E5%25AE%2588&h=59978694\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191103/s00001/1572758184297/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E3%80%8C%E8%A1%8C%E8%A1%97%E3%80%8D-%E6%B7%BB%E9%A6%AC%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89-%E9%BA%A5%E8%8A%B1%E8%87%A3%E9%81%8A%E6%A8%82%E5%A0%B4%E6%9C%89%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E9%A7%90%E5%AE%88</a>"},{"pid":"ce3e559b4e1c821cdfa97bc6e9dd37bdd056ca0d","tid":1690140,"uid":45089,"like":92,"dislike":1,"score":91,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:24:51.000Z","msg":"馬逢國有特權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad01e784eab089676d2d22093e9c3c701be4eb78","tid":1690140,"uid":189,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"全城戒嚴，老友記同賓賓都要返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a48ca3af8d2ed84d7f774c41232fd4278f5aa7","tid":1690140,"uid":127929,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:29:01.000Z","msg":"自己人放行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ef76087a71b779eb23d15189f219fc852855df","tid":1690140,"uid":240362,"like